{"tid":315371,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"在日2年 已厭倦","createTime":"2017-07-10T03:29:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T03:40:54.000Z","uid":35031,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"753cabac526ec497820b21c63fe1ef310da76183","tid":315371,"uid":35031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:29:13.000Z","msg":"已經留左係日本2年 （工作簽證）<br />\n基本上可以去既地方都去哂（県黎計係得福島同佐賀無留過...8月青春18去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n已經對日本的景點厭倦 去到邊都一樣樣（特別係d 穴場景點 根本到到都一樣唔係睇廟就睇海...）<br />\n購物的話不嬲網購為主 返香港叫人転送都一樣買到<br />\n生活的話有比香港好亦有比香港差的地方<br />\n滿員電車加加齡臭同驚比人屈痴漢係最驚的地方<br />\n<br />\n雖然份工係國際大公司 但收入扣稅同保險後同香港差唔多 普通新卒價<br />\n但香港唔駛交租（同屋企人住） 反而儲更多<br />\n<br />\n完全無朋友 去親邊都一個人 好孤獨<br />\n日文麻麻（2年前N5咁黎 而家叫pass左N1 工作文件睇同寫都無問題 係会話有困難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n英文同普通話都好差<br />\n<br />\n開始好想返去了<br />\n但又驚返去唔會搵到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n爭扎左成年 而家基本上都決心返一返去<br />\n<br />\n如果真係無工可能再決定返唔返去日本再搵吧（都一定係無前途既工架喇）<br />\n不過日本作為外國人長住真心唔好受<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ccc900f23369ff13aee4f068a32ab1377fc68a","tid":315371,"uid":87196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:31:42.000Z","msg":"邊行呀"},{"pid":"02ee7144cc99cd43b622dd172a9b74e37134eaab","tid":315371,"uid":35031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:36:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊行呀</blockquote><br />\n算係IT又算係翻譯又算係文員咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 低技術工種<br />\n因為上司全日本人但工作文件係中文 得圍內知有冇做錯所以完全無壓力亦唔會有獎賞 <br />\n好hea但基本上全日都唔會講到一句野（打字就極多、日文打字速度應該而家pass到派遣d 19打字test<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n完全自閉工"},{"pid":"925c6e3f33fbc23309fc7a2a864eced8430a58bf","tid":315371,"uid":27307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T01:30:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊行呀</blockquote><br />\n算係IT又算係翻譯又算係文員咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 低技術工種<br />\n因為上司全日本人但工作文件係中文 得圍內知有冇做錯所以完全無壓力亦唔會有獎賞 <br />\n好hea但基本上全日都唔會講到一句野（打字就極多、日文打字速度應該而家pass到派遣d 19打字test<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n完全自閉工</blockquote><br />\n你咪算好囉, 有得hea<br />\n我又要對客, 又要對內 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有自閉工不知幾好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1458d8b55d9cad1acbd94d5f1b088fcabf528f0e","tid":315371,"uid":27307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T01:33:07.000Z","msg":"你本身讀咩, 做咩會去左日本 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6a6c68665e54507a17e5d706679c0a006867b2","tid":315371,"uid":5313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T01:38:57.000Z","msg":"番到黎搵番D日文相關工作應該易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c752db8c7547847ba9ed89ac54ed0fcf11d9d0","tid":315371,"uid":38143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T01:44:31.000Z","msg":"冇housing咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a2f7622f95add3611e448a8c1fb92cffda4f75","tid":315371,"uid":27307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T07:04:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇housing咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n除非係傳統大公司, 通常都冇"},{"pid":"7351f416f442484ffc8f92c5e59846682d6677e6","tid":315371,"uid":23833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T07:06:42.000Z","msg":"食日本妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fe4d240e692072dafa60c47cdf7e6979f276166","tid":315371,"uid":1367,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-