方都去過哂🤣<br />\n但次次一個人去<br />\n展覽自己一個去<br />\n食飯自己一個食<br />\n幾好幾靚都好無聊😞<br />\n<br />\n人工就...唔算低唔算高咁<br />\n不過交稅交到痴線<br />\n一個月1/4人工冇左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eda8c766612969f89091965831c97ba22b388b05","tid":315371,"uid":42326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T10:19:27.000Z","msg":"如果想搵類你呢d類低技術但又似半文員咁<br />\n點搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHello work有冇"},{"pid":"1c0b5a165c581c9eb747a945ba7611901235c1ee","tid":315371,"uid":158295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:40:54.000Z","msg":"樓主, 我最近批左第二期日本WH<br />\n追緊你問我答個post<br />\n有冇LINE/ TG 可以做個朋友?"}]}